metadata.name: Tree Of Life #22
metadata.description: The project “Tree of Life“ marks a new beginning for Somewhere. The tree serves as a powerful metaphor for fresh starts, growth, and the interconnectedness of all living beings. Its roots, firmly anchored in the ground, represent the strength and stability necessary for embarking on a fresh chapter in life. The branches reaching skyward embody the boundless opportunities and aspirations that await those who embrace change.
